00:59:49.094 --> 00:59:51.963
The film? What can I say?
I didn't like it.


641
00:59:52.064 --> 00:59:54.032
It was very unpleasant...

642
00:59:54.733 --> 00:59:56.635
but it's a great film.

643
00:59:56.702 --> 01:00:00.272
It's astonishing

644
01:00:00.339 --> 01:00:03.308
because of how it's made

