01:00:03.375 --> 01:00:05.777
and the genius behind it.

646
01:00:05.844 --> 01:00:07.212
I absolutely loved it.

647
01:00:07.579 --> 01:00:11.616
I don't know if I should say this...
but I found it really funny.


648
01:00:12.484 --> 01:00:15.854
I really enjoyed myself
and the end is great.


649
01:00:24.363 --> 01:00:27.699
When the screening was over
everyone started clapping


650
01:00:27.766 --> 01:00:33.338
but nothing untoward happened.

